{"tid":2195662,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"必也正名 - 古德明","createTime":"2020-09-09T10:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T10:19:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3f04372549be4e51f19db722932c264803797e63","tid":2195662,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:19:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200909/PVMR4THHFFBPDORNCM4GJFCQE4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200909%2FPVMR4THHFFBPDORNCM4GJFCQE4%2F&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg0yCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=7da63707\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200909%2FPVMR4THHFFBPDORNCM4GJFCQE4%2F&h=584db6ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200909/PVMR4THHFFBPDORNCM4GJFCQE4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n必也正名 - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0gqFbaj210doOwWQ-_2cQPM2Mho=/1240x710/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Y4F24SFLENCGRH44MQBLIMVEJQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0gqFbaj210doOwWQ-_2cQPM2Mho%3D%2F1240x710%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FY4F24SFLENCGRH44MQBLIMVEJQ.png&h=c25e682f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《蘋果日報》截圖<br />\n<br />\n美國眾議員佩里（Scott Perry）最近提出《為敵正名法案（Name the Enemy Act ）》，反對稱中共「國家主席」為president，這當然是因為「總統」英文叫president，而「國家主席」則應是state chairman，不可混為一談。他還說：「稱中國元首為president（總統），使人誤會其權力經民主選舉賦與。」<br />\n<br />\n「國家主席」不應稱為president，我二零一二年七月四日已在《真情假意》文中指出；美國人現在才發覺譯名不妥貼，未免遲鈍。而習近平私淑毛澤東，毛澤東既以「Chairman Mao（毛主席）」之名聞於英語國家，則習近平改稱「Chairman Xi（習主席）」，將名實兩得其宜，遠勝馬鹿易形的「President Xi（習總統）」。<br />\n<br />\n孔子主張「必也正名」，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n現在，「正名」在中國幾乎無人懂得是什麼。。。。。。"}]}